datasets.name: f17bdd35
datasets.query:
WITH 
profile_metrics AS (
  SELECT * FROM `amine_elhelou`.`monitoring_dq`.`silver_transaction_predictions_profile_metrics`
   WHERE window.start >= :`Time Window Start` AND window.end <= :`Time Window End` -- limit to the inspection time window range
  AND isnull(slice_key) AND isnull(slice_value) -- default to "No Slice"
  AND `ModelVersion` = "*" -- default to all model ids
),
last_window_in_inspection_range AS (
  SELECT window.start AS Window, granularity AS Granularity FROM profile_metrics
  WHERE window.start = (SELECT MAX(window.start) FROM profile_metrics) 
  ORDER BY Granularity LIMIT 1 -- order to ensure the `granularity` selected is stable
),
profile_metrics_inspected AS (
  SELECT * FROM profile_metrics
  WHERE Granularity = (SELECT Granularity FROM last_window_in_inspection_range)
)
SELECT
  window.start AS Window,
  granularity AS Granularity,
  COALESCE(slice_key, "No slice") AS `Slice key`,
  COALESCE(slice_value, "No slice") AS `Slice value`,
  `ModelVersion` AS `Model Id`,
  * EXCEPT(window, granularity, slice_key, slice_value)
FROM profile_metrics_inspected
WHERE
  log_type = "INPUT"
  AND quantiles IS NOT NULL
  AND column_name != ":table"
  AND Granularity = (SELECT Granularity FROM last_window_in_inspection_range)
ORDER BY window.start DESC

datasets.name: d0c766a8
datasets.query:
WITH 
profile_metrics AS (
  SELECT * FROM `amine_elhelou`.`monitoring_dq`.`silver_transaction_predictions_profile_metrics`
   WHERE window.start >= :`Time Window Start` AND window.end <= :`Time Window End` -- limit to the inspection time window range
  AND isnull(slice_key) AND isnull(slice_value) -- default to "No Slice"
  AND `ModelVersion` = "*" -- default to all model ids
  AND column_name NOT IN (":table", "Prediction", "ProductRating") -- filter out non feature column
),
last_window_in_inspection_range AS (
  SELECT window.start AS Window, granularity AS Granularity FROM profile_metrics
  WHERE window.start = (SELECT MAX(window.start) FROM profile_metrics) 
  ORDER BY Granularity LIMIT 1 -- order to ensure the `granularity` selected is stable
),
profile_metrics_inspected AS (
  SELECT * FROM profile_metrics
  WHERE Granularity = (SELECT Granularity FROM last_window_in_inspection_range)
),
feature_integrity_last_window AS (
  SELECT
    column_name,
    percent_null,
    percent_zeros,
    percent_nan,
    -- CHANGE THRESHOLD BELOW TO TUNE THE SENSITIVITY OF THE QUERY
    CAST(percent_null >=5 AS INT) AS has_high_nulls,
    CAST(percent_zeros >=5 AS INT) AS has_high_zeros,
    CAST(percent_nan >=5 AS INT) AS has_high_nan,
    --
    num_nulls,
    window.start AS Window,
    granularity AS Granularity,
    COALESCE(slice_key, "No slice") AS `Slice key`,
    COALESCE(slice_value, "No slice") AS `Slice value`,
    `ModelVersion` AS `Model Id`
  FROM profile_metrics_inspected
  WHERE
    log_type = "INPUT"
    AND window.start = (SELECT Window FROM last_window_in_inspection_range) -- limit to last window
    AND Granularity = (SELECT Granularity FROM last_window_in_inspection_range)
)
SELECT 
  Window,
  Granularity,
  `Slice key`,
  `Slice value`,
  `Model Id`,
  sum(has_high_nulls), 
  sum(has_high_zeros), 
  sum(has_high_nan)
FROM feature_integrity_last_window
GROUP BY 1,2,3,4,5

datasets.name: c6d6500a
datasets.query:
WITH 
profile_metrics_inspected AS (
  SELECT * FROM `amine_elhelou`.`monitoring_dq`.`silver_transaction_predictions_profile_metrics`
   WHERE window.start >= :`Time Window Start` AND window.end <= :`Time Window End` -- limit to the inspection time window range
  AND isnull(slice_key) AND isnull(slice_value) -- default to "No Slice"
  AND `ModelVersion` = "*" -- default to all model ids
  AND column_name NOT IN (":table", "Prediction", "ProductRating") -- filter out non feature column
),
drift_metrics_inspected AS (
  SELECT * FROM `amine_elhelou`.`monitoring_dq`.`silver_transaction_predictions_drift_metrics`
   WHERE window.start >= :`Time Window Start` AND window.end <= :`Time Window End` -- limit to the inspection time window range
  AND isnull(slice_key) AND isnull(slice_value) -- default to "No Slice"
  AND `ModelVersion` = "*" -- default to all model ids
),
last_window_in_inspection_range AS (
  SELECT window.start AS Window, granularity AS Granularity FROM profile_metrics_inspected
  WHERE window.start = (SELECT MAX(window.start) FROM profile_metrics_inspected) 
  ORDER BY Granularity LIMIT 1 -- order to ensure the `granularity` selected is stable
)
SELECT 
  concat(window.start," - ", window.end) AS Window,
  granularity AS Granularity,
  COALESCE(slice_key, "No slice") AS `Slice key`,
  COALESCE(slice_value, "No slice") AS `Slice value`,
  `ModelVersion` AS `Model Id`,
  --
  -- CHANGE METRIC AND THRESHOLDs BELOW TO TUNE DRIFT DETECTION
  --
  SUM(IF(chi_squared_test.pvalue < 0.05,1,0)) AS count
FROM drift_metrics_inspected
WHERE ks_test is NULL -- limit to categorical columns
AND drift_type = "CONSECUTIVE" -- only consider consecutive drift
AND window.start = (SELECT Window FROM last_window_in_inspection_range)
AND Granularity = (SELECT Granularity FROM last_window_in_inspection_range)
GROUP BY 1,2,3,4,5

datasets.name: 1f31b450
datasets.query:
WITH 
profile_metrics AS (
  SELECT * FROM `amine_elhelou`.`monitoring_dq`.`silver_transaction_predictions_profile_metrics`
   WHERE window.start >= :`Time Window Start` AND window.end <= :`Time Window End` -- limit to the inspection time window range
  AND isnull(slice_key) AND isnull(slice_value) -- default to "No Slice"
  AND `ModelVersion` = "*" -- default to all model ids
  AND column_name NOT IN (":table", "Prediction", "ProductRating") -- filter out non feature column
),
latest_two_windows_in_inspection_range AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT window.start AS Window
    FROM profile_metrics
    ORDER BY Window DESC LIMIT 2
),
granularity_selected AS (
  SELECT granularity AS Granularity FROM profile_metrics
  WHERE window.start = (SELECT MAX(window.start) FROM profile_metrics) 
  ORDER BY Granularity LIMIT 1 -- order to ensure the `granularity` selected is stable
),
drift_metrics_inspected AS (
  SELECT * FROM `amine_elhelou`.`monitoring_dq`.`silver_transaction_predictions_drift_metrics`
   WHERE Granularity = (SELECT Granularity FROM granularity_selected)
  AND window.start >= :`Time Window Start` AND window.end <= :`Time Window End` -- limit to the inspection time window range
  AND isnull(slice_key) AND isnull(slice_value) -- default to "No Slice"
  AND `ModelVersion` = "*" -- default to all model ids
),
numerical_cols_high_drift AS (
  SELECT column_name
  FROM drift_metrics_inspected
  WHERE ks_test is NOT NULL -- limit to numerical columns
    
    -- CHANGE METRIC AND THRESHOLDs BELOW TO TUNE DRIFT DETECTION
    
    AND ks_test.pvalue < 0.05
    AND drift_type = "CONSECUTIVE" -- only consider consecutive drift
    AND window.start = (SELECT max(Window) FROM latest_two_windows_in_inspection_range) -- limit to last window
    AND column_name != ":table"
),
profile_metrics_inspected AS (
  SELECT * FROM profile_metrics
  WHERE Granularity = (SELECT Granularity FROM granularity_selected)
  AND window.start IN (SELECT Window FROM latest_two_windows_in_inspection_range) -- limit to last two windows
  AND column_name in (SELECT column_name FROM numerical_cols_high_drift) -- limit to columns with high drift
),
latest_two_window_quantiles AS (
  SELECT window.start AS Window, 
  column_name, quantiles
  FROM profile_metrics_inspected
  WHERE isnotnull(quantiles)
),
baseline_profile_metrics_inspected AS (
  SELECT * FROM `amine_elhelou`.`monitoring_dq`.`silver_transaction_predictions_profile_metrics`
   WHERE log_type = "BASELINE"
  AND isnull(slice_key) AND isnull(slice_value) -- default to "No Slice"
  AND `ModelVersion` = "*" -- default to all model ids
  AND column_name in (SELECT column_name FROM numerical_cols_high_drift) -- limit to columns with high drift
),
baseline_quantiles AS (
  SELECT column_name, quantiles
  FROM baseline_profile_metrics_inspected
  WHERE isnotnull(quantiles)
),
latest_two_window_quantiles_exploded AS (
    SELECT Window,
    column_name,
    explode_outer(transform(quantiles, ((value, index) -> (index / 1000 AS quantile,value)))) AS temp
    FROM latest_two_window_quantiles
),
baseline_quantiles_exploded as (
    select "Baseline" As Window,
    column_name,
    explode_outer(transform(quantiles, ((value, index) -> (index / 1000 as quantile,value)))) as temp
    from baseline_quantiles
)
SELECT * EXCEPT(temp), temp.* FROM latest_two_window_quantiles_exploded
UNION ALL
SELECT * EXCEPT(temp), temp.* FROM baseline_quantiles_exploded;

datasets.name: aa1f332d
datasets.query:
WITH 
profile_metrics AS (
  SELECT * FROM `amine_elhelou`.`monitoring_dq`.`silver_transaction_predictions_profile_metrics`
   WHERE window.start >= :`Time Window Start` AND window.end <= :`Time Window End` -- limit to the inspection time window range
  AND isnull(slice_key) AND isnull(slice_value) -- default to "No Slice"
  AND `ModelVersion` = "*" -- default to all model ids
),
last_window_in_inspection_range AS (
  SELECT window.start AS Window, granularity AS Granularity FROM profile_metrics
  WHERE window.start = (SELECT MAX(window.start) FROM profile_metrics) 
  ORDER BY Granularity LIMIT 1 -- order to ensure the `granularity` selected is stable
),
profile_metrics_inspected AS (
  SELECT * FROM profile_metrics
  WHERE Granularity = (SELECT Granularity FROM last_window_in_inspection_range)
),
table_profile_over_time AS (
SELECT
  window.start AS Window,
  granularity AS Granularity,
  COALESCE(slice_key, "No slice") AS `Slice key`,
  COALESCE(slice_value, "No slice") AS `Slice value`,
  `ModelVersion` AS `Model Id`,
  * EXCEPT(window, granularity, slice_key, slice_value, `ModelVersion`)
FROM profile_metrics_inspected
WHERE
  log_type = "INPUT"
  AND column_name = ":table"),
threshold AS (
  SELECT 
  Granularity, 
  `Slice key`, 
  `Slice value`, 
  `Model Id`,
  median(count) AS threshold 
  FROM table_profile_over_time 
  GROUP BY 1,2,3,4
  )
SELECT df2.threshold, df1.*
FROM table_profile_over_time df1 
LEFT JOIN threshold df2 
ON df1.Granularity = df2.Granularity
AND df1.`Slice key`=df2.`Slice key`
AND df1.`Slice value`=df2.`Slice value`
AND df1.`Model Id`=df2.`Model Id`

  SELECT window.start AS Window, granularity AS Granularity FROM profile_metrics
  WHERE window.start = (SELECT MAX(window.start) FROM profile_metrics) 
  ORDER BY Granularity LIMIT 1 -- order to ensure the `granularity` selected is stable
),
profile_metrics_inspected AS (
  SELECT * FROM profile_metrics
  WHERE Granularity = (SELECT Granularity FROM last_window_in_inspection_range)
)
SELECT
  element_at(quantiles, int(size(quantiles) * 0.25)) AS p25,
  element_at(quantiles, int(size(quantiles) * 0.5)) AS p50,
  element_at(quantiles, int(size(quantiles) * 0.75)) AS p75,
  element_at(quantiles, int(size(quantiles) * 0.9)) AS p90,
  window.start AS window,
  granularity AS Granularity,
  `ModelVersion` AS `Model Id`,
  COALESCE(slice_key, "No slice") AS `Slice key`,
  COALESCE(slice_value, "No slice") AS `Slice value`
FROM profile_metrics_inspected
WHERE
  log_type = "INPUT"
  AND quantiles IS NOT NULL
  AND column_name = "Prediction"
   AND Granularity = (SELECT Granularity FROM last_window_in_inspection_range)
ORDER BY window.start DESC

datasets.name: 34e18cf1
datasets.query:
WITH 
profile_metrics_inspected AS (
  SELECT * FROM `amine_elhelou`.`monitoring_dq`.`silver_transaction_predictions_profile_metrics`
   WHERE window.start >= :`Time Window Start` AND window.end <= :`Time Window End` -- limit to the inspection time window range
  AND isnull(slice_key) AND isnull(slice_value) -- default to "No Slice"
  AND `ModelVersion` = "*" -- default to all model ids
  AND column_name NOT IN (":table", "Prediction", "ProductRating") -- filter out non feature column
),
drift_metrics_inspected AS (
  SELECT * FROM `amine_elhelou`.`monitoring_dq`.`silver_transaction_predictions_drift_metrics`
   WHERE window.start >= :`Time Window Start` AND window.end <= :`Time Window End` -- limit to the inspection time window range
  AND isnull(slice_key) AND isnull(slice_value) -- default to "No Slice"
  AND `ModelVersion` = "*" -- default to all model ids
),
last_window_in_inspection_range AS (
  SELECT window.start AS Window, granularity AS Granularity FROM profile_metrics_inspected
  WHERE window.start = (SELECT MAX(window.start) FROM profile_metrics_inspected) 
  ORDER BY Granularity LIMIT 1 -- order to ensure the `granularity` selected is stable
),
exploded_frequent_items AS (
	SELECT
		EXPLODE(frequent_items) AS frequent_item,
		* EXCEPT (frequent_items)
	FROM profile_metrics_inspected
),
frequency_over_time AS (
SELECT
	column_name,
	COALESCE(CAST(frequent_item.item AS STRING), "null")  AS value,
	frequent_item.count AS count,
	count AS total_count,
	window.start AS Window,
  granularity AS Granularity,
  COALESCE(slice_key, "No slice") AS `Slice key`,
  COALESCE(slice_value, "No slice") AS `Slice value`,
  `ModelVersion` AS `Model Id`
FROM exploded_frequent_items
WHERE log_type = "INPUT"),
categorical_cols_high_drift AS (
	SELECT column_name 
	FROM drift_metrics_inspected
	WHERE chi_squared_test.pvalue < 0.05
  	AND drift_type = "CONSECUTIVE" -- only consider consecutive drift
  	AND window.start = (SELECT Window FROM last_window_in_inspection_range) -- limit to last window
  	AND column_name != ":table"
),
frequency_rank_last_window AS (
	SELECT 
	-- identifiers
	column_name, Granularity, `Slice key`, `Slice value`, `Model Id`,
	value, count, 
	dense_rank() over (
	partition by (column_name, Granularity, `Slice key`, `Slice value`, `Model Id`) 
	ORDER BY count DESC, value asc
	) AS frequency_rank
	FROM frequency_over_time
	WHERE Window = (SELECT Window FROM last_window_in_inspection_range) -- limit to last window
	AND column_name IN (SELECT * FROM categorical_cols_high_drift)
)

SELECT 
	df1.*, df1.count / df1.total_count AS percent
FROM frequency_over_time df1 JOIN 
(SELECT * FROM frequency_rank_last_window WHERE frequency_rank <= :top_k) df2
ON df1.column_name = df2.column_name 
AND df1.Granularity = df2.Granularity
AND df1.`Slice key` = df2.`Slice key`
AND df1.`Slice value` = df2.`Slice value`
AND df1.`Model Id` = df2.`Model Id`
AND df1.value = df2.value

datasets.name: adef1335
datasets.query:
WITH 
profile_metrics AS (
  SELECT * FROM `amine_elhelou`.`monitoring_dq`.`silver_transaction_predictions_profile_metrics`
   WHERE window.start >= :`Time Window Start` AND window.end <= :`Time Window End` -- limit to the inspection time window range
  AND isnull(slice_key) AND isnull(slice_value) -- default to "No Slice"
  AND `ModelVersion` = "*" -- default to all model ids
  AND column_name = "Prediction"
 ),
latest_two_windows_in_inspection_range AS (
    SELECT DISTINCT window.start AS Window
    FROM profile_metrics
    ORDER BY Window DESC LIMIT 2
),
granularity_selected AS (
  SELECT granularity AS Granularity FROM profile_metrics
  WHERE window.start = (SELECT MAX(window.start) FROM profile_metrics) 
  ORDER BY Granularity LIMIT 1 -- order to ensure the `granularity` selected is stable
),
drift_metrics_inspected AS (
  SELECT * FROM `amine_elhelou`.`monitoring_dq`.`silver_transaction_predictions_drift_metrics`
   WHERE Granularity = (SELECT Granularity FROM granularity_selected)
  AND window.start >= :`Time Window Start` AND window.end <= :`Time Window End` -- limit to the inspection time window range
  AND isnull(slice_key) AND isnull(slice_value) -- default to "No Slice"
  AND `ModelVersion` = "*" -- default to all model ids
),
profile_metrics_inspected AS (
  SELECT * FROM profile_metrics
  WHERE Granularity = (SELECT Granularity FROM granularity_selected)
  AND window.start IN (SELECT Window FROM latest_two_windows_in_inspection_range) -- limit to last two windows
),
latest_two_window_quantiles AS (
  SELECT window.start AS Window, 
  column_name, quantiles
  FROM profile_metrics_inspected
  WHERE isnotnull(quantiles)
),
baseline_profile_metrics_inspected AS (
  SELECT * FROM `amine_elhelou`.`monitoring_dq`.`silver_transaction_predictions_profile_metrics`
   WHERE log_type = "BASELINE"
  AND isnull(slice_key) AND isnull(slice_value) -- default to "No Slice"
  AND `ModelVersion` = "*" -- default to all model ids
  AND column_name = "Prediction"
 ),
baseline_quantiles AS (
  SELECT column_name, quantiles
  FROM baseline_profile_metrics_inspected
  WHERE isnotnull(quantiles)
),
latest_two_window_quantiles_exploded AS (
    SELECT Window,
    column_name,
    explode_outer(transform(quantiles, ((value, index) -> (index / 1000 AS quantile,value)))) AS temp
    FROM latest_two_window_quantiles
),
baseline_quantiles_exploded as (
    select "Baseline" As Window,
    column_name,
    explode_outer(transform(quantiles, ((value, index) -> (index / 1000 as quantile,value)))) as temp
    from baseline_quantiles
)
SELECT * EXCEPT(temp), temp.* FROM latest_two_window_quantiles_exploded
UNION ALL
SELECT * EXCEPT(temp), temp.* FROM baseline_quantiles_exploded;
